  tenant       Tenant   @relation(fields: [tenantId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime @updatedAt

  /// One SSO config row per (tenant, identity provider). A tenant binds to Google Workspace ONCE with their own clientId/secret. Different tenants of course own separate Google Workspace tenants and separate Microsoft Entra IDs.
